<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Item_definition_structure_arm  Entity: Assembled_part_association  
   <express_ref linkend="item_definition_structure:arm:Item_definition_structure_arm.Assembled_part_association"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Item_definition_structure_arm.Assembled_part_association">
An <b>Assembled_part_association</b> is the relation between an <b>Assembly_definition</b> and a <b>prt_occurrence_select</b> representing a constituent of the assembly. The <b>Assembly_definition</b> and the <b>Part_view_definition</b> that serves as 'definition' of the <b>Product_occurrence</b> shall share at least one Application_context. 
<note> The constituent may also be an assembly.</note>
An <b>Assembly_part_association</b> is a type of <b>Assembly_component_relationship</b> and <b>Occurrence_definition_relationship</b>

</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Item_definition_structure_arm  Entity: Assembled_part_association  Attribute: relating_view 
   <express_ref linkend="item_definition_structure:arm:Item_definition_structure_arm.Assembled_part_association.relating_view"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Item_definition_structure_arm.Assembled_part_association.relating_view">
The <b>relating_view</b> specifies the <b>Assembly_definition</b> that has subordinate constituents.
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Item_definition_structure_arm  Entity: Assembled_part_association  Attribute: related_view 
   <express_ref linkend="item_definition_structure:arm:Item_definition_structure_arm.Assembled_part_association.related_view"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Item_definition_structure_arm.Assembled_part_association.related_view">
The <b>related_view</b> specifies the <b>Product_occurrence</b> that is part of the <b>Occurrence_definition_relationship</b>. 
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Item_definition_structure_arm  Entity: Assembly_definition  
   <express_ref linkend="item_definition_structure:arm:Item_definition_structure_arm.Assembly_definition"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Item_definition_structure_arm.Assembly_definition">
An <b>Assembly_definition</b> is a definition of an <b>Item_version</b> that contains other subordinate objects.
An <b>Assembly_definition</b> is a subtype of <b>Part_view_definition</b>.

</ext_description>
